title: 05/01/2013 - The Church Of What's Happening Now #76
description:
Rudy Sarzo, legendary bassist who has played with Ozzy Osbourne, Quiet Riot, and Whitesnake, to name a few, calls in. We were also lucky enough to have comedy legend Bobby Slayton calll in.
